{"tid":856183,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 摺機 Galaxy F 預計 2019 年初發表","createTime":"2018-10-10T12:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T06:49:42.000Z","uid":52215,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"383d1885d1a1f12467e73a34f3613b95c6d10ca1","tid":856183,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"Samsung 摺機 Galaxy F 預計 2019 年初發表<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/203100_b4bcde3f0bfe33e631c4b329631cc3bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F203100_b4bcde3f0bfe33e631c4b329631cc3bb.jpg&h=628e25c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/203101_1a069ed66b90d593c67f8c53e6acf005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F203101_1a069ed66b90d593c67f8c53e6acf005.jpg&h=23a510c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n上月，Samsung 流動產品部門總裁 DJ Koh 曾經對外透露 Samsung 的首部可摺曲手機、即暫名為 Galaxy F 的新機種將會在今年 11 月正式登場。但據最新消息指出，Samsung 在 11 月 7 日的開發者大會之上公佈的，大有可能只是此機的部份規格，而非產品真身。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n按照目前消息所得，Samsung 最快都要在 2019 年初的兩大展覽 － CES 或 MWC 之上帶來 Galaxy F，其時大家還可以見到下一代的正統旗艦 Galaxy 10 及 Galaxy 10+。<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy F 現在已在開發當中，但進展如何其實未有確切證據，在網絡上依然未見有任何類似實機的流出，我們只能從小道消息中推測它將會採用可摺曲屏幕，據說在展開時可以達到 7.3 吋大、而摺疊後則為 4.6 吋。由於需要迎合屈曲屬性，Galaxy F 的機面將不會採用傳統玻璃材質，而是另一種由日本住友電子生產的透明合成物料。"},{"pid":"9932262df2a5d91beec18d3536500a33aa7a936c","tid":856183,"uid":2133,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:48:49.000Z","msg":"等睇步g flex後塵"},{"pid":"37925f0a02fad0cb53000d10d3fa15792167d286","tid":856183,"uid":43839,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9932262df2a5d91beec18d3536500a33aa7a936c","tid":856183,"uid":2133,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:48:49.000Z","msg":"等睇步g 